init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the other people who share your feelings, and you realize that you're all going to have the same life over and over again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They start shouting and throwing popcorn.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The lights come on, and a man in a white shirt steps out onto the stage, holding an antiquated wireless microphone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We are trying to help you, but we can't if you won't cooperate.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: 'We offer you several opportunities to change your life for the better, and we expect you to take advantage of those opportunities.
